        "type": "Omissions - Omission Legal Contradiction",
        "original_text": "This Agreement shall be governed in all respects by the laws of the Commonwealth of Australia and by the laws of the St ate of Victoria; as such laws are applied to agreem ents entered into and to be performed entirely within Au stralia.",
        "changed_text": "This Agreement shall be governed in all respects by the laws determined solely by the Society.",
        "explanation": "This change removes the legally defined jurisdiction and replaces it with a unilateral determination by the Society. This can violate Australian consumer protection laws regarding jurisdiction clauses that unfairly disadvantage consumers.",
